title: Announcing Woodbury 2015 New Talent Competition Winners! (Woodbury University)
text: ( Source : Woodbury University ) Three Woodbury animation seniors and one alumna will be featured at CTNX Animation Expo this November 20-22, 2015 . Woodbury Animation is proud to announce the winners of the 2015 New Talent Competition . Each
